				<div id="mw-content-text" lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr"><div class="metadata topicon nopopups" id="protected-icon" style="display:none; right:55px;"><a href="Wikipedia_Protection_policy#semi" title="This article is semi-protected."><img alt="Page semi-protected" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Padlock-silver.svg/20px-Padlock-silver.svg.png" width="20" height="20" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Padlock-silver.svg/30px-Padlock-silver.svg.png 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/f/fc/Padlock-silver.svg/40px-Padlock-silver.svg.png 2x" /></a></div>
<table class="infobox vevent" style="float: right; clear: right; width: 315px; border-spacing: 2px; text-align: left; font-size: 90%;">
<tr>
<th class="summary" colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 110%;">Vietnam War<br />
<small>(Chiến tranh Việt Nam)</small></th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="background-color: #DCDCDC; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle;">Part of the <a href="Indochina_Wars" title="Indochina Wars">Indochina Wars</a> and the <a href="Cold_War" title="Cold War">Cold War</a></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2" style="text-align: center; font-size: 90%; border-bottom: 1px solid #aaa; line-height: 1.5em;"><a href="http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/File:Bruce_Crandall's_UH-1D.jpg" class="image"><img alt="Bruce Crandall's UH-1D.jpg" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/Bruce_Crandall's_UH-1D.jpg/300px-Bruce_Crandall's_UH-1D.jpg" width="300" height="209" srcset="//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/Bruce_Crandall%27s_UH-1D.jpg/450px-Bruce_Crandall%27s_UH-1D.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/76/Bruce_Crandall%27s_UH-1D.jpg/600px-Bruce_Crandall%27s_UH-1D.jpg 2x" /></a><br />
A <a href="Bell_UH-1_Iroquois" title="Bell UH-1 Iroquois">Bell UH-1D helicopter</a> piloted by Major <a href="../Bruce_P._Crandall" title="Bruce P. Crandall">Bruce P. Crandall</a> climbs skyward after discharging a load of U.S. infantrymen on a <a href="Search_and_destroy" title="Search and destroy">search and destroy</a> mission</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td colspan="2">
<table style="width:100%; margin:0; padding:0; border:0">
<tr>
<th style="padding-right:1em">Date</th>
<td>1 November 1955<span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="bday dtstart published updated">1955-11-01</span>)</span><sup id="cite_ref-start_date_1-0" class="reference"><a href="#cite_note-start_date-1"><span>[</span>A 1<span>]</span></a></sup> – 30&#160;April&#160;1975<span style="display:none">&#160;(<span class="dtend">1975-04-30</span>)</span><br />
(19 years,&#160;5 months,&#160;4 weeks&#160;and&#160;1 day)</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right:1em">Location</th>
<td><span class="location"><a href="South_Vietnam" title="South Vietnam">South Vietnam</a>, <a href="North_Vietnam" title="North Vietnam">North Vietnam</a>, <a href="Cambodia" title="Cambodia">Cambodia</a>, <a href="Laos" title="Laos">Laos</a></span></td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right:1em">Result</th>
<td><a href="North_Vietnam" title="North Vietnam">North Vietnamese</a> victory
<ul>
<li>Withdrawal of <a href="United_States_Armed_Forces" title="United States Armed Forces">American forces</a> from <a href="Indochina" title="Indochina">Indochina</a></li>
<li>Communist governments take power in <a href="Provisional_Revolutionary_Government_of_the_Republic_of_South_Vietnam" title="Provisional Revolutionary Government of the Republic of South Vietnam">South Vietnam</a>, <a href="Democratic_Kampuchea" title="Democratic Kampuchea">Cambodia</a> and <a href="Laos" title="Laos">Laos</a></li>
<li><a href="South_Vietnam" title="South Vietnam">South Vietnam</a> is annexed by <a href="North_Vietnam" title="North Vietnam">North Vietnam</a></li>
</ul>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th style="padding-right:1em">Territorial<br />
changes</th>
<td>Unification of North and South Vietnam into the <a href="Vietnam" title="Vietnam">Socialist Republic of Vietnam</a>.</td>
</tr>
</table>
</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<th colspan="2" style="background-color: #B0C4DE; text-align: center; vertical-align: middle; font-size: 110%;">Belligerents</th>
</tr>
<tr>
